  "description": "Crystal growth is invisible at human timescales — hold a note for 2 seconds and the tone blooms into its full harmonic structure like time-lapse crystallography. Very high formant intensity (0.90) means each note arrives as a seed and grows outward into its overtone lattice. Poly4 lets four crystal formations coexist in the same sonic space, each blooming at its own rate. A geology of sound, patient and inevitable.",
